      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm also looking at the ingredients on this brand i found. it has a lot of \"animal by-products\" and \"rendered meal\" listed near the top. is that actually okay for an older dog or should i be looking for something more specific like whole meat sources?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
