      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While \"animal by-products\" and \"rendered meal\" are legal ingredients, for an aging dog, it is generally better to prioritize foods listing specific, named whole meat sources higher up on the ingredient list. These named meats, like \"chicken,\" \"beef,\" or \"salmon,\" offer more transparency regarding the quality and digestibility of the protein. You should aim for a diet that reflects a whole-food approach for your senior Lab.",
